<Layout title="Yaratıcı Yıkım - Fractional Product Leadership">
  
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Yaratıcı Yıkım</h1>
    <h2>Fractional Product Leadership for Fast-Growing Companies</h2>
    <p>Transforming ambitious ideas into scalable products through strategic disruption and disciplined execution.</p>
    <p class="author"><strong>Tahir Murat Tortopoğlu</strong><br/>
    Product Strategy · Business Model Innovation · Fractional CPO/Head of Product</p>
    <a href="#contact" class="cta-button">Get in Touch →</a>
  </section>

  <!-- CREATIVE DESTRUCTION -->
  <section class="section">
    <h2>What is Yaratıcı Yıkım?</h2>
    <p><strong>"Creative Destruction"</strong> — a term coined by economist Joseph Schumpeter — describes capitalism's engine of innovation: creating new value by dismantling outdated structures.</p>
    <p>In modern business, this means <strong>building products, business models, and strategies that challenge the status quo</strong>.</p>
    <p>My approach embodies this philosophy:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Question existing assumptions</li>
      <li>Make bold, data-informed decisions</li>
      <li>Create sustainable competitive advantages</li>
    </ul>
    <p><strong>Yaratıcı Yıkım</strong> isn't just about innovation—it's about <strong>delivering the right innovation, at the right time, in the right way.</strong></p>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="section services">
    <h2>Services</h2>
    
    <div class="service-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Fractional Product Leadership</h3>
        <p>Part-time or project-based CPO/Head of Product support:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>0-to-1 product strategy and roadmap design</li>
          <li>Product-market fit validation</li>
          <li>Agile transformation and team alignment</li>
          <li>Stakeholder management (board, investors, customers)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Business Model Innovation</h3>
        <p>Business model design for sustainable growth:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Revenue model optimization</li>
          <li>Unit economics analysis</li>
          <li>Pricing strategy</li>
          <li>Go-to-market planning</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Product Strategy Workshops</h3>
        <p>Action-oriented workshops that align your teams:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Discovery & opportunity mapping</li>
          <li>OKR/roadmap planning sessions</li>
          <li>Competitive positioning</li>
          <li>Feature prioritization frameworks</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <h3>Consulting & Advisory</h3>
        <p>Custom consulting and training:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Product management coaching</li>
          <li>Due diligence support (investors/M&A)</li>
          <li>Process optimization</li>
          <li>Tailored training programs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TRUSTED BY -->
  <section class="section clients">
    <h2>Trusted By</h2>
    <p>Organizations I've worked with include:</p>
    
    <div class="client-list">
      <div class="client">
        <h4>Özyeğin University</h4>
        <p>Academic program development and strategic planning</p>
      </div>
      <div class="client">
        <h4>METU Technopolis</h4>
        <p>Startup mentoring and product advisory</p>
      </div>
      <div class="client">
        <h4>Kuartis</h4>
        <p>Product strategy and business model optimization</p>
      </div>
      <div class="client">
        <h4>Sovos Türkiye/Foriba</h4>
        <p>Enterprise SaaS product development and tax compliance solutions</p>
      </div>
      <div class="client">
        <h4>Mükellef Teknoloji</h4>
        <p>FinTech product strategy and platform growth</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="capabilities">
      <h3>Core Capabilities:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Strategic Leadership:</strong> Translating business vision into actionable product roadmaps</li>
        <li><strong>Execution Excellence:</strong> Driving cross-functional teams from concept to launch</li>
        <li><strong>Team Building & Management:</strong> Coaching product teams and establishing scalable processes</li>
        <li><strong>Stakeholder Alignment:</strong> Bridging executive vision, engineering reality, and customer needs</li>
        <li><strong>Data-Driven Decision Making:</strong> Balancing qualitative insights with quantitative validation</li>
      </ul>
      <p><strong>Technical Fluency:</strong> HubSpot ecosystems, PHP/Laravel stack, Google Workspace, API integrations</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="section about">
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>I'm <strong>Tahir Murat Tortopoğlu</strong>, a product strategist and fractional product leader helping fast-growing companies build products that matter.</p>
    <p>With a background spanning <strong>SaaS product management, business model design, and technical education</strong>, I bridge the gap between vision and execution.</p>
    <p>My approach combines:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Strategic thinking</strong> rooted in Schumpeterian creative destruction</li>
      <li><strong>Hands-on execution</strong> with modern product frameworks</li>
      <li><strong>Cross-functional leadership</strong> across tech, business, and education</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Based in the Netherlands, I work with international teams building ambitious products across multiple industries.</p>
    <p class="registration"><strong>Registered:</strong><br/>
    KVK: 99326868<br/>
    SBI Code: 70202 (Business and Management Consultancy)</p>
  </section>

 <!-- CONTACT -->
  <section id="contact" class="section contact">
    <h2>Let's Talk</h2>
    <p>Whether you need fractional product leadership, strategic advisory, or workshop facilitation—let's explore how we can work together.</p>
    
    <div class="contact-info">
      <p><strong>Tahir Murat Tortopoğlu</strong><br/>
